adventurer.personality_description:
You are sentimental.
You are concrete: you prefer dealing with the world as it is, rarely considering abstract ideas. You are imaginative: you have a wild imagination. And you are demure: you prefer to listen than to talk, especially in group situations.
Your choices are driven by a desire for sophistication.
You consider both achieving success and tradition to guide a large part of what you do. You seek out opportunities to improve yourself and demonstrate that you are a capable person. And you highly respect the groups you belong to and follow their guidance.
